{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-blog-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/blog/how-to-get-the-site-locale-in-concrete-5/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>This is how you get the site locale in Concrete 5</p>\n<p>In the controller</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$site</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token property\">app</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token function\">make</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'site'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token function\">getSite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$defaultLocale</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$site</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token function\">getDefaultLocale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$defaultLocaleCode</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$defaultLocale</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token function\">getLocale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// This sets the variable so you can access it in the view</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'defaultLocaleCode'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$defaultLocaleCode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the view</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token function\">var_dump</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$defaultLocaleCode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// en_GB</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"07, February 2022","title":"How to get the site locale in Concrete 5"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"dfc29699-4c2d-58db-ba83-5f0bdd8dd016","frontmatter__slug":"/how-to-get-the-site-locale-in-concrete-5","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"how-to-get-the-site-locale-in-concrete-5"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}